&lt;p&gt;Objetivos:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class="simple"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Probar &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://github.com/getnikola/nikola"&gt;Nikola&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;em&gt;metiendo mano&lt;/em&gt;).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Practicar &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ReStructuredText"&gt;reStructuredText&lt;/a&gt; y &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Markdown"&gt;Markdown&lt;/a&gt;  (a ver si consigo que mi documentación quede más &lt;a class="reference external" href="http://www.wordreference.com/sinonimos/emperifollado"&gt;emperifollada&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Para escribir/editar los posts estoy usando &lt;a class="reference external" href="http://www.sublimetext.com/3"&gt;Sublime Text 3 Beta&lt;/a&gt; junto con el plugin &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://github.com/mgaitan/sublime-rst-completion"&gt;Restructured Text (RST) Snippets&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid>http://ssebastianj.github.io/en/posts/probando-nikola-en-github-pages.html</guid><pubDate>Wed, 28 May 2014 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>